    <div class="body">
        <p>In some RDBMS, the database's describe table query reports whether a column is auto-increment.  For example, in MySQL the "Extra" column returned by {{DESC</p>

<p>&lt;</p>

<p>table&gt;}} reports a string "auto_increment" for such a column.</p>

